{"tid":712514,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"The Rock狄維莊遜7月訪港 行紅地墊同香港觀眾見面","createTime":"2018-06-22T06:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T02:14:17.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cb7c2fabe06eb076a06663401c3a4b430ad5990b","tid":712514,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:55:02.000Z","msg":"荷里活動作巨星「The Rock」狄維莊遜 (Dwayne Johnson)殺到嚟香港！其新作《高凶浩劫》（Skyscraper）將於7月12號上映，故事以一座位於香港嘅摩天大樓作背景。因此戲中主要演員，包括狄維莊遜及「天王嫂」昆凌都將會於7月5至7日來港宣傳。香港為是次電影宣傳首站兼全球記者會地點，到時主角狄維莊遜、台灣「天王嫂」昆凌、於戲中飾演THe Rock妻子嘅莉芙甘寶 (Neve Campbell) 、一對小童星挪亞哥特利 (Noah Cottrell)及麥克納羅拔絲(McKenna Roberts )、荷里活華裔演員文峰、新加坡演員黃經漢、導演羅遜馬素費巴(Rawson Marshall Thurber) 及兩位編劇包費林 (Beau Flynn ) 、海雲加西亞(Hiram Garcia) 將遠道而來。<br />\n<br />\n《高凶浩劫》台前幕後齊齊現身香港，除咗參加全球記者會，仲會出席紅地墊活動及粉絲見面會。大會更安排狄維莊遜於《高凶浩劫》粉絲特別放映會同來自世界各地嘅支持者近距離接觸。此外，於3日嘅訪港之旅中，狄維莊遜及其他演員還會於香港四圍出沒，與多個媒體拍攝特備節目，例如去到天際100觀景台欣賞維港景色及乘搭電車穿梭香港街道等，市民將有機會於香港街頭遇上The Rock！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180622/large/1529645610_4524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180622%2Flarge%2F1529645610_4524.jpg&h=186ac31b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180622/58349867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F58349867&d=sll77SUCa11LyytIORsnJv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2a0f9a94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180622%2F58349867&h=714fd1e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180622/58349867</a>"},{"pid":"23f2f1635d9bacf5c708b4ec8ab063e4ee555f2b","tid":712514,"uid":77788,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"053da9c1d035aa4772f3babb47c277f43df8